                <div class=3D"cred-title">M.S. Emergency Management =E2=80=
=94 University of Southern California</div>
                <div class=3D"cred-desc">Graduate program in emergency mana=
gement with focus on all-hazards preparedness, response, and recovery. Expe=
cted Fall 2026.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class=3D"cred-item">
              <div class=3D"cred-icon">=F0=9F=9B=A1</div>
