=94 FireGuard Remote Sensing Program</div>
                <div class=3D"cred-desc">Built and scaled a remote sensing =
and geospatial intelligence capability delivering satellite imagery and geo=
spatial products to CAL FIRE, FEMA, and state EOCs during major disasters.<=
/div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class=3D"cred-item">
              <div class=3D"cred-icon">=F0=9F=94=A5</div>
